Ty si celý čas vedel, že mali s Bu
Puo Shangom taký zvláštny vzťah?

255
00:17:08,740 --> 00:17:11,840
Aký je ten ich vzťah?

256
00:17:11,850 --> 00:17:14,210
Prečo sa hneváš?

257
00:17:17,710 --> 00:17:20,070
<i>Hnevám sa?{\i}</i>

258
00:17:36,520 --> 00:17:37,680
Čo ti tak trvalo?

259
00:17:37,690 --> 00:17:39,290
Prepáč.

260
00:17:46,480 --> 00:17:48,290
Videla si to?

261
00:17:48,300 --> 00:17:50,750
Pobozkal sestričku Qin!

262
00:17:52,910 --> 00:17:55,170
Dobre, odpustím ti.

263
00:17:55,310 --> 00:17:57,160
Poďme tam.

264
00:18:05,100 --> 00:18:08,360
Chcela by som, aby aj mňa
Qin tak kŕmila hotdogom.

265
